extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em LocalLibrary], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Books:] 
        span.badge !{data.book_count}
      li #[strong Copies:] 
        span.badge !{data.book_instance_count}
      li #[strong Copies available:] 
        span.badge !{data.book_instance_available_count} 
      li #[strong Authors:] 
        span.badge !{data.author_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] 
        span.badge !{data.genre_count}